We do not sell, rent, or share your data with third parties.

3Ô∏è‚É£ Data Storage

All economy and user data are stored locally in a database file (islamic_economy.db).

No external servers or cloud databases are used.

Only the bot owner has access to this data.

If the database is reset, your virtual currency and progress may be permanently deleted.

4Ô∏è‚É£ Data Removal

If you wish to have your stored data deleted:

Contact the bot owner via Discord with your User ID.

Your record will be manually removed from the database.

Once deleted, your economy progress and other data cannot be recovered.

5Ô∏è‚É£ Security

We take data security seriously:

Tokens, API keys, and credentials are stored securely in .env files and never shared.

The bot runs in a controlled environment to prevent unauthorized access.

However, please understand that no system is completely immune to security risks.

